Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.46,Default,man,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.46,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.81,Default,man,0,0,0,,Still not interested, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.81,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,また興味なしってか?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:29.68,Default,man,0,0,0,,Hey, why are we letting him live?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:29.68,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,な なんで生かしとくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:31.63,Default,man,0,0,0,,He killed the don.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:31.63,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ドンをやりやったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:32.88,Default,man,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:32.88,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,知るか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.22,Default,man,0,0,0,,Florida, a paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.22,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,憧れのフロリダ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:40.59,Default,man,0,0,0,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:40.59,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,くだらね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.61,Default,man,0,0,0,,That's the end of the Vanettis, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.61,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ヴァネッティも もう終わりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:49.40,Default,man,0,0,0,,It's perfect for the presentation of Don Strega.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:49.40,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ドン ストレーガのお披露目にはお誂え向き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:54.70,Default,man,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:54.70,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,おい やめとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:57.17,Default,man,0,0,0,,What's the big deal? He's not gonna eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:57.17,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,いいだろう どうせ食わねんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:00.13,Default,man,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:00.13,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,じゃ早速
