Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.43,Default,man,0,0,0,,Throw down your weapons and come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.43,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,武器を捨てて出てこい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.37,Default,man,0,0,0,,If you do as we say, we won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.37,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,おとなしく従えば 悪いようにはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.95,Default,man,0,0,0,,Please, don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.95,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,頼む 打たないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.69,Default,man,0,0,0,,We're coming out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.69,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,今から出て行く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.60,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Those Galassia guys keep coming in swarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.60,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ガラッシアの野郎ともわんさか来やがって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.06,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Even if all our bullets hit, we wouldn't have enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.06,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,全部当たっても タマが足りね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.97,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そろそろ頃合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.72,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sticking it out any longer won't—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.72,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,これ以上粘っても...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.27,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.27,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:12.15,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Hotel Lawless. Room 501.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:12.15,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ホテル ローレス 501号室だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.52,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Everyone's been sent over to the Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.52,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,皆アイランドにであらってるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.98,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.98,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,行くのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, you guys should get out of here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.74,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前らもここを出ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Who wants to die in the same place Fango did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴの死に場所でくたばるなんて ぞっとしね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.00,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.00,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:32.37,Default,tig,0,0,0,,You're the one they're after, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:32.37,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,そもそも あいつらのお目当てはお前だしね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.68,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.68,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,な ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.66,Default,tig,0,0,0,,This will be our...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.66,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,これが俺たちの...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.13,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.13,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,まぁ いいや...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.86,Default,tig,0,0,0,,When you see him, sock him one for me too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.86,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,やつに会ったら 俺の分も殴っておいてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.96,Default,cer,0,0,0,,So, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.96,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,さて どこ行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.96,Default,cer,0,0,0,,There's no way we can get away from the Galassias anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.96,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,どうせ ガラッシアから逃げ切れねけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.00,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.00,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なんでお前がここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:23.01,Default,cer,0,0,0,,What about you? Why are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:23.01,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そういうお前は なんで生きてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.17,Default,cer,0,0,0,,You wanted revenge against the Vanettis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.17,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ヴァネッティの奴等に復讐したがったんだよう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.00,Default,cer,0,0,0,,And you finished that crap already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.00,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そんなもん もうとっくに終わってんじゃねか?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.85,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.85,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,おい 聞いてんのかよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:38.52,Default,cer,0,0,0,,He never wanted to join the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:38.52,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,あいつはな ファミリーなんかに入りたくなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.84,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,わざわざ儲け話持ってってやっても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.44,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Even when I told him how rich he could get,\N he wouldn't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.44,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,見向きもしね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.34,Default,cer,0,0,0,,It was stupid how damn straight-laced he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.34,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,バカみたいに真面目な奴だった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:51.10,Default,cer,0,0,0,,But you... You drove him crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:51.10,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,なのに お前のせいでおかしくなっちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.83,Default,cer,0,0,0,,You killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.83,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,お前に殺されちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.52,Default,cer,0,0,0,,He'd never even been with a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.52,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,女も知らねのに...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.78,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,あいつが死んでお前が生きてんのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:02.61,Default,cer,0,0,0,,How is it right that you live and he dies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.61,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,なんか可笑しくねか?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.76,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.02,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,聞いてんのかよ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.36,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.36,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,うるすうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.55,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Who's the one who sent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.55,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,差出人は誰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,Ganzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.99,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ガンゾ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:24.72,Default,nero,0,0,0,,So I was being deceived from all sides, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:24.72,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,寄ってたかって騙されてたって訳か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.90,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,テスタラグーザの息子がこの手紙を受け取って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:30.99,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The son of Testa Lagusa received\N this letter and returned to Lawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.99,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ローレスに戻ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.53,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.53,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そして...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.76,Default,av,0,0,0,,Frate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.76,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,フラテも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.79,Default,av,0,0,0,,Volpe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.79,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ボルペも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.01,Default,av,0,0,0,,Del Toro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.01,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,デルトルも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.25,Default,av,0,0,0,,Barbero...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.25,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,バルベルも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:43.76,Default,av,0,0,0,,Vanno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:43.76,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,フンノも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.05,Default,av,0,0,0,,I killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.05,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,皆俺が殺した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:53.89,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm the only person named in this letter who's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:53.89,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,この手紙の中で 生き残ってるのは俺一人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.83,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なぜやらなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.82,Default,av,0,0,0,,Vincent holed up in his mansion and wouldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.82,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ヴィンセントは屋敷に籠って出てこない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.28,Default,av,0,0,0,,Obviously, I had to get close to his son first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.28,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,まずその息子に近づくのは当然だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That day, at the playhouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あの日 劇場で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:20.11,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have needed me alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:20.11,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,もう俺を生かしておく必要はなかったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:26.47,Default,av,0,0,0,,I wanted you and Vincent to feel the same pain I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:26.47,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,お前とヴィンセントには俺と同じ苦しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:30.30,Default,av,0,0,0,,A pain worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:30.30,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,死ぬ以上の苦しみを与えるつもりだった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.41,Default,av,0,0,0,,A shame Vincent died so soon though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.41,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,残念ながら ヴィンセントはくたばったけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.49,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I-Idiot! Don't start that here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.49,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ばばばがやろう こんなとこでおっぱじめんじゃねい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:04.71,Default,av,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:04.71,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,やれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.52,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'll save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お預けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.52,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Acting like he understands everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,悟ったような面しやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.77,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Sheesh... You mafia guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.77,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ったく マフィアってやつは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.21,Default,tig,0,0,0,,That's the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.21,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,きくな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.36,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Here, a pick-me-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.36,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ほれ 景気付けに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.96,Default,tig,0,0,0,,You know the saying? "Choke on your wine, you'll make it out fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.96,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,知ってるか 酒で噎せると生き残るってと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.67,Default,tig,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.67,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,心配ずね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.68,Default,man,0,0,0,,Mr. Tigre...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.68,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,テグルさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.38,Default,man,0,0,0,,The boat's all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.38,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,艇の準備ができました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.39,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Great. Now it's goodbye, Lawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.39,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,これでローレスはおさらばで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.74,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.74,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,先に行け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:13.69,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.75,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Go! Run for the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.75,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,行け 船まで走るだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:29.56,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm right here! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:29.56,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ほらほら こっちだ かかってこいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.45,Default,man,0,0,0,,Hey, take another look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.45,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,おい もう一回見てこい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:12.26,Default,str,0,0,0,,The king's arms are long, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:12.26,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,王の手は長いぞ ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.21,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Want to get some breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.21,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そろそろ朝飯でも食うぐあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Awfully trusting, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.06,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お人好しの野郎だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.30,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Hey, are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.30,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,おい まじか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.04,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,は ちょ は...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.18,Default,cer,0,0,0,,You two! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.18,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,お前ら おい...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.02,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Wait! Wh-What? What? What?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.02,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ちょ なななに おい ちょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.69,Default,cer,0,0,0,,A-Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.69,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ま まじか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.55,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.55,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,腹減った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.25,Default,str,0,0,0,,Why did you shoot Don Galassia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.25,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,なぜ ドンガラシアを撃った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.57,Default,av,0,0,0,,He had a good, full life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.57,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もう十分人生を楽しんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.17,Default,av,0,0,0,,He was in high spirits to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.17,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,最後まで上機嫌だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.10,Default,str,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.10,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.99,Default,av,0,0,0,,It was convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.99,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,都合が良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.90,Default,av,0,0,0,,The Vanettis killed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.90,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺はバネッチィの奴らに家族を殺された
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:05.42,Default,str,0,0,0,,And now we're crushing the Vanettis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:05.42,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,そのバネッチィは俺たちに潰される
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.40,Default,str,0,0,0,,You really manipulated all of us, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.40,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,まんまとお前に利用されたってわけだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.13,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.13,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何故助けた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.15,Default,str,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.15,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,礼が言いたくてなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.71,Default,str,0,0,0,,I'm the next don.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.71,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,次のドンは俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.23,Default,str,0,0,0,,You really sped up my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.23,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,お前のおかげで随分予定が早まった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.20,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,危ねぇじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.93,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Shut up and start shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.93,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,うるせ  黙って撃ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.37,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,くそやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.67,Default,str,0,0,0,,The Vanettis fled to the Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.91,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,バネッチィの奴らはアイランドに逃げ込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.11,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,お前が寝てる間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.11,Default,str,0,0,0,,While you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.91,Default,av,0,0,0,,Prohibition will end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.91,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もうすぐ禁酒法も終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.69,Default,av,0,0,0,,That town won't be worth anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.69,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんな町にはなんの価値もなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.79,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.79,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なんでわざわざ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:59.02,Default,str,0,0,0,,Nero killed Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:59.02,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,ネロはロナルドの敵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:04.08,Default,str,0,0,0,,But I think you might be more useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:04.08,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,だが使いみちはお前のほうが有りそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.19,Default,str,0,0,0,,being a man with no inconvenient ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.19,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,余計な野心もない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:12.17,Default,str,0,0,0,,If you kill a certain someone over there, you can be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:12.17,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,あそこにる誰かさんをやれば お前は自由になれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.87,Default,str,0,0,0,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.87,通用720日文-ja,str,0,0,0,,一緒に来るか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.71,Default,av,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.71,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もう どうでもいいことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,うまそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm escorting a dangerous prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.97,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,凶悪犯を護送中だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.95,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Best not to stare at him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.95,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あんまジロジロ見ない方がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:04.22,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Everyone who's gotten involved with him has ended up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:04.22,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,此奴に関わった奴は みんな死んじまった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.00,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Good meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.00,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ご馳走さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:14.92,Default,av,0,0,0,,Go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:14.92,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,右だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.75,Default,av,0,0,0,,Go south, and you'll end up on Route 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.75,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,南に向かえば41号に出る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.81,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どこに行くつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.58,Default,av,0,0,0,,The ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.58,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.65,Default,av,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.65,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,見たことあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:50.23,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just leave the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:50.23,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なんで さっさと町を出なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.88,Default,av,0,0,0,,I wanted to see my revenge play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.88,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,復讐を見届ける為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Were you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,満足したか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:12.15,Default,av,0,0,0,,I thought that by completing my revenge and making my family's killers pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:12.15,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,復讐を果たし 家族の死に報いれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.87,Default,av,0,0,0,,I would find a reason to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.87,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,生きる理由を取り戻せると思った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,But there was nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.02,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だが何も残らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.91,Default,av,0,0,0,,It was all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.91,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,すべては無駄事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.58,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ふざけんなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.11,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Don't you dare try to sum it all up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.11,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そんな言葉で片付けじゃねぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:45.47,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What about them?! What were their deaths for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:45.47,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,彼奴等は 彼奴等の死は一体なんだったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.54,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.54,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なんで俺殺さなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I trusted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前を信じてたんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.07,Default,av,0,0,0,,Then you should have just killed me back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.07,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だったら俺をあの時殺してれば良かっただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.21,Default,av,0,0,0,,That night, seven years ago...
